  <brief_title>Use of Injectable-platelet-rich-fibrin (I-PRF) to Thicken Gingival Phenotype</brief_title>
  <official_title>New Approach to Increasing Gingival Thickness in Individuals With Fine Gingival Phenotype:Injectable Platelet Rich Fibrin (I-PRF)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
